        <h1> @Resource.toEat </h1>

        @*<p>When following a ketogenic diet, meals and snacks should center around the following foods:</p>*@
        <ul>
            <li> @Resource.Eggs2  @*Eggs: Pastured, organic whole eggs make the best choice.*@</li>
